- configure proper networking
- install bind9 with master/slave
- restrict clients by source networks
- allow zone transfers only from slave
- choose your startup name
- create a db:
 - A records for intra01,infra02
 - CNAMES for ns1,ns2
 - ns.<startup> should return 2 IPs
- dns records should come from variables
- every dns records updates should increase serial numbers
